<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #6f42c1; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; }
        .badge { background: #6f42c1; color: white; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Bella Couture</h1>
            <h2>Mise a jour de commande</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour <strong>{{ order.customerName }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Le statut de votre commande <strong>{{ order.orderNumber }}</strong> a ete mis a jour.</p>
            <p>Statut actuel : <span class="badge">{{ order.statusLabel }}</span></p>
            <p>Total : <strong>{{ order.total|number_format(2) }} DT</strong></p>
            <p>Merci pour votre confiance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
